snippet.description:
"The Kerala Story" is a recently released movie by director Sudipto Sen that has been surrounded by controversy. The movie revolves around the story of four women from Kerala who converted to Islam and joined a militant organisation. However, there are questions about whether this movie represents the truth or propaganda. What is the truth behind the story being conveyed in this movie? Is something being hidden from us? Tere Bin Episode 43 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Nisa Hair Removal Cream - 10th May 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Nisa Hair Removal Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 3767 - Bhide To Leave Gokuldham?! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | ‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï ‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada

snippet.description:

We add basil seeds and King coconut meat to make this juice as healthy drink! The taste is divine!

snippet.description:

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: Moment former Pakistan PM Imran Khan is arrested
snippet.description:
Imran Khan, the former prime minister of Pakistan, has been arrested by the military as he appeared in court in Islamabad to face charges in a corruption case. 
Subscribe to Guardian News on YouTube ‚ñ∫ http://bit.ly/guardianwiressub

Fawad Chaudhry, a senior official with Khan‚Äôs Pakistan Tehreek-e-Insaf party, said the 72-year-old was arrested on Tuesday by agents from the National Accountability Bureau, the country‚Äôs anti-corruption body. A Reuters witness said that shortly after Khan entered through the gate of the Islamabad high court, contingents of paramilitary forces and armoured personnel carriers entered after him.

snippet.title: Oppenheimer | New Trailer
snippet.description:
Oppenheimer - Only In Theaters 7 21 23

Written and directed by Christopher Nolan, Oppenheimer is an IMAX¬Æ-shot epic thriller that thrusts audiences into the pulse-pounding paradox of the enigmatic man who must risk destroying the world in order to save it. 
 
The film stars Cillian Murphy as J. Robert Oppenheimer and Emily Blunt as his wife, biologist and botanist Katherine ‚ÄúKitty‚Äù Oppenheimer. Oscar¬Æ winner Matt Damon portrays General Leslie Groves Jr., director of the Manhattan Project, and Robert Downey, Jr. plays Lewis Strauss, a founding commissioner of the U.S. Atomic Energy Commission. 
 
Academy Award¬Æ nominee Florence Pugh plays psychiatrist Jean Tatlock, Benny Safdie plays theoretical physicist Edward Teller, Michael Angarano plays Robert Serber and Josh Hartnett plays pioneering American nuclear scientist Ernest Lawrence.
 
Oppenheimer also stars Oscar¬Æ winner Rami Malek and reunites Nolan with eight-time Oscar¬Æ nominated actor, writer and filmmaker Kenneth Branagh. 
 
The cast includes Dane DeHaan (Valerian and the City of a Thousand Planets), Dylan Arnold (Halloween franchise), David Krumholtz (The Ballad of Buster Scruggs), Alden Ehrenreich (Solo: A Star Wars Story) and Matthew Modine (The Dark Knight Rises). 
 
The film is based on the Pulitzer Prize-winning book American Prometheus: The Triumph and Tragedy of J. Robert Oppenheimer by Kai Bird and the late Martin J. Sherwin. The film is produced by Emma Thomas, Atlas Entertainment‚Äôs Charles Roven and Christopher Nolan. 

Oppenheimer is filmed in a combination of IMAX¬Æ 65mm and 65mm large-format film photography including, for the first time ever, sections in IMAX¬Æ black and white analogue photography. 

Nolan‚Äôs films, including Tenet, Dunkirk, Interstellar, Inception and The Dark Knight trilogy, have earned more than $5 billion at the global box office and have been awarded 11 Oscars and 36 nominations, including two Best Picture nominations.

snippet.title: Tere Bin Episode 44 Teaser - 10th May 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 44 Teaser - 10th May 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

snippet.title: MEG 2: THE TRENCH - OFFICIAL TRAILER
snippet.description:
They‚Äôre back for seconds. #Meg2 only in theaters August 4.

Get ready for the ultimate adrenaline rush this summer in ‚ÄúMeg 2: The Trench,‚Äù a literally larger-than-life thrill ride that supersizes the 2018 blockbuster and takes the action to higher heights and even greater depths with multiple massive Megs and so much more! Dive into uncharted waters with Jason Statham and global action icon Wu Jing as they lead a daring research team on an exploratory dive into the deepest depths of the ocean. Their voyage spirals into chaos when a malevolent mining operation threatens their mission and forces them into a high-stakes battle for survival. Pitted against colossal Megs and relentless environmental plunderers, our heroes must outrun, outsmart, and outswim their merciless predators in a pulse-pounding race against time. Immerse yourself in the most electrifying cinematic experience of the year with ‚ÄúMeg 2: The Trench‚Äù ‚Äì where the depths of the ocean are matched only by the heights of sheer, unstoppable excitement!

Warner Bros. Pictures and CMC Pictures present ‚ÄúMeg 2: The Trench,‚Äù with Statham and Jing headlining an ensemble cast that also includes Sophia Cai (‚ÄúThe Meg‚Äù), Page Kennedy (‚ÄúThe Meg‚Äù), Sergio Peris-Mencheta (‚ÄúRambo: Last Blood‚Äù), Skyler Samuels (‚ÄúThe Gifted‚Äù), and Cliff Curtis (‚ÄúAvatar‚Äù franchise).
‚ÄúMeg 2: The Trench‚Äù is directed by Ben Wheatley (‚ÄúIn the Earth,‚Äù ‚ÄúFree Fire‚Äù), from a screenplay by Jon Hoeber & Erich Hoeber (‚ÄúThe Meg,‚Äù ‚ÄúTransformers: Rise of the Beasts‚Äù) and Dean Georgaris (‚ÄúThe Meg,‚Äù ‚ÄúLara Croft: Toom Raider ‚Äì The Cradle of Life‚Äù), and a screen story by Dean Georgaris and Jon Hoeber & Erich Hoeber, based on the novel The Trench by Steve Alten. The film is produced by Lorenzo di Bonaventura (‚ÄúThe Meg,‚Äù ‚ÄúBumblebee‚Äù) and Belle Avery (‚ÄúThe Meg,‚Äù ‚ÄúBefore the Devil Knows You‚Äôre Dead‚Äù), and executive produced by Jason Statham, Cate Adams, Ruigang Li, Catherine Xujun Ying, Wu Jing, E. Bennett Walsh, Erik Howsam, Gerald R. Molen and Randy Greenberg. 

Joining director Wheatley behind the camera are director of photography Haris Zambarloukous (‚ÄúBelfast,‚Äù ‚ÄúMurder on the Orient Express‚Äù), production designer Chris Lowe (‚ÄúThe Gray Man,‚Äù ‚ÄúNo Time to Die‚Äù) and editor Jonathan Amos (‚ÄúBaby Driver,‚Äù ‚ÄúPaddington 2‚Äù). The visual effects supervisor is Pete Bebb (‚ÄúFantastic Beasts and Where to Find Them,‚Äù ‚ÄúInception‚Äù), and costume designer is Lindsay Pugh (‚ÄúThe Matrix Resurrections,‚Äù ‚ÄúKrypton‚Äù). The music is by Harry Gregson-Williams (‚ÄúThe Meg,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Martian‚Äù).

Warner Bros. Pictures and CMC Pictures present, in association with DF Pictures, a di Bonaventura/Apelles Entertainment, Inc. production, a Ben Wheatley film, ‚ÄúMeg 2: The Trench.‚Äù It will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures and is set to open in theaters in North America on August 4, 2023 and internationally beginning 02 August 2023.

snippet.title: Rista Rista | Mohsin Khan | Divya Agarwal | Stebin Ben | Dharma 2.O | Gourov Dasgupta | Shellee
snippet.description:

snippet.title: Why is Manipur violence dangerous for India? | Manipur riots explained | Abhi and Niyu
snippet.description:
In this video, we will explore the causes and consequences of the 2023 Manipur violence, an ongoing ethnic clash between the Hindu Meitei people and Christian tribal Kuki people in India‚Äôs north-eastern state of Manipur. The violence erupted on 3 May 2023 during the ‚ÄúTribal Solidarity March‚Äù called by the All Tribal Student Union Manipur (ATSUM) to protest the granting of reservations to the majority Meitei community1. The violence killed at least 60 people, and injured at least a further 230. It also resulted in the burning of 25 churches and the displacement of 23,000 people. The Indian Army and the Assam Rifles were deployed to restore law and order, and a shoot-at-sight order was issued in some areas. Internet services were also suspended for five days. We will examine the historical and political background of the conflict, which involves land rights, religious differences, and identity politics. We will also look at the current situation and the prospects for peace and reconciliation in this volatile region.

Please like, share, and subscribe to our channel for more videos on current affairs and social issues. Thank you for watching!

#Manipur #NorthEast #abhiandniyu

snippet.description:
Episode 37645: Tapu Ka Proposal
--------------------------------------------------------
The parents of a girl named Sonu come to see Bhide and tell him how their daughter eloped with her boyfriend. Bhide is anxious about Sonu because of this. When Madhavi receives a call from Anjali informing her of the Mahila Mandali meeting, she makes haste there. Bhide is instructed to wait since Madhavi is expecting a significant mango delivery. Sonu doesn't answer the phone when Bhide tries to call her, so he sets out to find her. Bhide eventually makes it to Lover's Park, where he sees Tapu bending over and giving Sonu a red rose. Follow along to discover more!

snippet.title: Big Achievement! Indian Rupee Finally Takes Over US Dollar | 18 Countries Agreed to Trade In Rupees
snippet.description: In this video, we explore the concept of internationalization of the Indian Rupee. The Indian Rupee is one of the fastest-growing currencies in the world, and with its growing popularity. We also discuss the benefits and challenges of internationalizing a currency, including increased global trade, reduced currency risk for businesses, and greater international influence for the issuing country. We consider the future prospects for the internationalization of the Indian Rupee and what steps the government and central bank may take to further promote its use in global transactions.

snippet.title: NEET 2023 Question Paper Discussion || Physics Wallah || NEET 2023 Answer Key
snippet.description:
Submit Your NEET Application - https://bit.ly/neet_YT
NEET MahaRevision : https://bit.ly/3N3LZ3y


Batch Details : 
- We will cover Botany, Zoology, Physics, Organic Chemistry, Inorganic Chemistry, and Physical Chemistry in One Shot

- One Shot Marathon series will start on Physics wallah - Alakh Pandey Channel on 19th April 2023

- Then, Subject wise Master MCQ Marathon series will be continue on Competition Wallah YouTube Channel on 26th April 2023

- At the end, 5 Live AITS (All India Test Series) Live Discussion on Competition Wallah YouTube Channel

- After NEET 2023 Exam, the Live Paper Discussion will also be scheduled on Competition Wallah YouTube Channel at the same day.

- Lecture notes will be available on NEET Maha Revision 2023 Batch (PW App)

- The complete course will be accessible to all the students until the NEET 2023 Exams

- Marathon Schedule will be provided in the community post of Competition Wallah YT Channel and Announcement section of the PW App

snippet.description:
On a BMTC bus, with the incredible women of Bengaluru | Rahul Gandhi | Karnataka.

Congress' 5 Guarantees

1. GRUHA JYOTHI - 200 units of free electricity every month to every household to help bear bills.

2. GRUHA LAKSHMI - ‚Çπ2,000 each month to the female head of every household for sustenance and help in the fight against price rise.

3. ANNA BHAGYA - 10 Kg rice, every month to every member of BPL families. No one in Karnataka will sleep hungry.

4. YUVA NIDHI - ‚Çπ3,000 every month to every unemployed graduate for a period of two years. And ‚Çπ1,500 to unemployed youths with Diploma. So, during the period they are finding a job, Congress govt will help them with income support.
